---
title: Game-Day Beef Chili with Borlotti Beans, Poblano Pepper, and Cheddar Cheese
description: If you’re looking for a recipe that’ll satisfy your whole team, chili is a sure bet. In this version, we’re keeping things simmering with ground beef, borlotti beans, poblano peppers, and our special Mexican spice blend, which has just the tiniest bit of heat. It’s mild enough for your kids to gobble up but has plenty of flavor to satisfy the adults—just break out the hot sauce if you like it scorching!
